<p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 1.8px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.6px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgba(252, 248, 243, 0.7); font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">为检验发展对象的理论知识储备和党性修养，严格把控党员发展“质量关”，端正发展对象入党动机。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 1.8px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgba(252, 248, 243, 0.7); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2.225em; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">2023年12月11日，经济管理学院在A10-314党员活动室开展了发展对象答辩会。党总支书记蔡平出席答辩会，党总支专职组织员周婷婷、学工办主任郭伟、党总支宣传委员杨磊、党总支统战委员丁瑞风、学生支部组织委员王艳萍以及学生支部宣传委员陈娴担任此次评委。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 1.8px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgba(252, 248, 243, 0.7); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2.225em; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240417/1713367633381077653.png" title="1713367633381077653.png" alt="image.png" width="500" height="294" style="width: 500px; height: 294px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1.8px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgba(252, 248, 243, 0.65); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2.225em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">在答辩开始前，蔡平书记寄语各发展对象，不管答辩的最终结果如何，希望大家都要继续以党员的标准严格要求自己，加强自身政治理论学习，提高专业素养与党性修养，同时在实践中锻炼自己，在为人民服务的行动中提升自己。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1.8px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgba(252, 248, 243, 0.65); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2.225em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">接着周婷婷老师为各位评审介绍了答辩过程和评分规则，各发展对象应分别从自我介绍、辩题阐述、现场提问等三方面进行答辩，并要求各位评审实事求是、公正客观。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1.8px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgba(252, 248, 243, 0.65); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2.225em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">随后，周婷婷老师宣布答辩正式开始，发展对象依次进行答辩。</span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 1.8px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgba(252, 248, 243, 0.7); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2.225em; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span><br/></p>